column47: The number of people who viewed your Page's videos for at least 10 seconds, or for nearly their total length if they're shorter than 10 seconds. During a single instance of a video playing, we'll exclude any time spent replaying the video.
column53: The number of times your videos played with sound on for at least 10 seconds, or for nearly their total length if they're shorter than 10 seconds. During a single instance of a video playing, we'll exclude any time spent replaying the video.

column47: The number of times your Page's videos replayed for at least 10 seconds, or for nearly their total length if they're shorter than 10 seconds.
column53: The number of times your videos played with sound on for at least 3 seconds, or for nearly their total length if they're shorter than 3 seconds. During a single instance of a video playing, we'll exclude any time spent replaying the video.

column47: The total time, in milliseconds, people viewed your Page's video.
